NAME
    Rit::Base - The ultimate database


DESCRIPTION
    Rit::Base implements an RDF like nodal network database


PREREQUISITIES
    Para::Frame, PostgreSQL and some other Perl modules.

    Some of the modules can be installed in debian:

    apt-get install libclone-perl libdbd-pg-perl libjson-perl libgraphviz-perl libtext-worddiff-perl

INSTALL

    You are not meant to install Rit::Base among your Perl
    libraries.  Copy the ditribution to /usr/local/rb
    See doc/INSTALL for details.


DEVELOPMENT
    ...


